            <p><em>Megaplanet 5.4</em> by <a href="http://emuseum.ringling.org/emuseum/people/7266/josh-simpson">Josh Simpson </a>(1989); Glass; 8 x 8 x 8 in. (20.3 x 20.3 x 20.3 cm)</p>
          </figcaption>
        
      
